BOULDER, Colo. (AP) -- Prosecutors posted a photograph of a   white, furry bear dressed as Santa Claus on an Internet site  Thursday in a plea for public help with the JonBenet Ramsey slaying  investigation.
BOULDER, Colo. (AP) -- JonBenet Ramsey's mother switched from   charming to tough when challenged by a detective, leading police to  believe she was ``capable of bringing harm to her daughter,''  author Lawrence Schiller writes in a new book on the crime.
